1. *Novolje* su neizbežne u životu. (Troubles are unavoidable in life.)
2. On je uvek u *nevoljama*. (He is always in trouble.)
3. Ona se nada da će se *nevolje* brzo završiti. (She hopes that the troubles will end soon.)
4. *Nevoljama* koje je proživela, naučila je lekciju. (From the troubles she went through, she learned a lesson.)
5. On je uhvaćen u *nevoljama*. (He was caught in trouble.)